cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.IT, cs.CC 

This paper deals with the study of languages and words, which falls under the category of formal languages (cs.FL). The paper also discusses algorithms for computing minimal forbidden factors, which involves data structures (cs.DS) and combinatorics (cs.DM). The paper also touches upon information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC) in the context of DFA minimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.FL, followed by cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.IT, and cs.CC.
